&quot;hahah, right, since when does sense heading cause me to take a flying leap from the boat&quot; <br>
&quot;it doesn't&quot;<br>
&quot;yes, that is my point&quot;<br>
5 minutes pass..<br>
&quot;Ehm, are you going to send a GM or guide out here to help me or something?&quot;<br>
&quot;The gods have spoken, there isn't anything i can do&quot;<br>
so now i don't know what is going on.<br>
&quot;Yeah, well ask Tunare, I'm sure she'll ask you to send a nice GM or guide out here and put me on a dock in this zone or something&quot;<br>
&quot;They have spoken, i am sorry&quot;<br>
so now I'm just pissed off.<br>
&quot;No! you are NOT sorry, this happen all the time to a lot of people every day, every hour. It happened all the time to my Druid, do you want to know why i never reported it?&quot;<br>
&quot;why?&quot;<br>
&quot;Because if i fall off, i can gate back to safety, all healers and casters Can, that's 2/3 of the population&quot;<br>
&quot;i can't help you, I'm sorry&quot;<br>
&quot;I'm not asking you to gate me to where i am going, and I'm not trying to trick you into gating me to where i am going, I'm asking to be put on a dock in this zone, a dock of your choice&quot;<br>
&quot;If you continue to harass me, i will call a GM, please let the matter drop&quot;<br>
so i tried to swim for it, died, petitioned, got a new one this time. This one tells me that i should have petitioned when i got knocked off the boat. Go figure, eh? <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgroverants.showPrevMessage?topicID=258.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgroverants.showNextMessage?topicID=258.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgroverants.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=258.topic><img src=http://dev.thedruidsgrove.org/images/forum/addreplya.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgroverants.emailToFriend?topicID=258.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgroverants.threadControl?topicID=258.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/gfx/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgroverants.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=258.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgroverants.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=258.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub13.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="thedruidsgrovegeneral">General - EQ<option value="thedruidsgrovefrm27">General - DAOC<option value="thedruidsgrovegeneralot">General - OT<opt